1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(The Two Top Male Models)

4
00:00:53,140 --> 00:00:54,500
(Pan Residence)

5
00:00:55,030 --> 00:00:56,350
All right.

6
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,920
Ever since I married
into the Pan family,

7
00:00:59,070 --> 00:01:00,560
I've been mistreated at every turn.

8
00:01:00,750 --> 00:01:02,670
What's the point of keeping this child?

9
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:04,280
I might as well die!

10
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,070
What are you doing?

11
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,840
Father. Mother.

12
00:01:09,350 --> 00:01:11,480
Muyan doesn't want
the Pan family's child anymore.

13
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:12,870
She wants to get rid of the baby.

14
00:01:12,870 --> 00:01:13,590
What?

15
00:01:14,590 --> 00:01:15,680
This...

16
00:01:17,950 --> 00:01:18,510
This...

17
00:01:18,790 --> 00:01:19,760
Muyan,

18
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,640
you mustn't act on impulse!

19
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:24,120
This is the Pan family's first child!

20
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,990
I don't want anything
to do with the Pan family.

21
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:26,870
Let me go!

22
00:01:27,350 --> 00:01:28,430
Muyan.

23
00:01:29,230 --> 00:01:30,480
It's my fault for failing you.

24
00:01:30,870 --> 00:01:32,350
Your injuries haven't healed yet.

25
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:34,190
You mustn't
put yourself through this again.

26
00:01:35,230 --> 00:01:35,920
That's right.

27
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:38,480
Just tell us what you want.

28
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,040
I'll make it happen.

29
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:41,100
Who are you trying to fool?

30
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:42,680
No...

31
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,580
- How about this?
- Let me go!

32
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,480
Let me go!

33
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,150
How about this?

34
00:01:45,350 --> 00:01:46,070
Muyan,

35
00:01:46,710 --> 00:01:48,120
once the baby is born,

36
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:50,280
I'll transfer the deed
to the Pan Residence

37
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:52,560
to my future grandson or granddaughter.

38
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:55,280
Then you won't
have anything to worry about.

39
00:01:55,790 --> 00:01:56,790
Master, this...

40
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:58,040
Fine.

41
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,560
Whether I'll even live

42
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,710
to see that day

43
00:02:01,710 --> 00:02:02,760
is another matter.

44
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:04,200
Then...

45
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,870
I'll transfer the deed to Yang.

46
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,280
Once you've given birth,

47
00:02:09,310 --> 00:02:12,030
we'll give it to you as our gift.

48
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,400
That's right, Muyan.

49
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,280
Father and Mother have both promised.

50
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,710
Please stay.

51
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,080
I'm begging you.

52
00:02:20,870 --> 00:02:22,310
This...

53
00:02:26,910 --> 00:02:28,430
But if I'm humiliated again,

54
00:02:28,470 --> 00:02:29,750
I'll leave this place for good.

55
00:02:29,750 --> 00:02:30,400
Good!

56
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,710
Good!

57
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,400
As long as you're staying.

58
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,680
As long as you're staying.

59
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:39,630
Good.

60
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:45,300
(On the Foolish Deeds of the Scoundrel
Crown Prince Zheng Yuanhe)

61
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,680
What are you staring at?

62
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:56,870
Read it.

63
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,560
On

64
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:05,400
the Foolish Deeds of the Scoundrel
Crown Prince Zheng Yuanhe.

65
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,400
Master,

66
00:03:08,710 --> 00:03:09,680
isn't that wording

67
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,710
a bit inappropriate?

68
00:03:17,390 --> 00:03:18,630
What's inappropriate about it?

69
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:20,680
Calling the Crown Prince

70
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:22,400
a scoundrel...

71
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:23,910
Besides,

72
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,120
although I've never met him,

73
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,560
his decision to shut down the rice balls

74
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,030
might have been

75
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:32,280
out of an abundance of concern
for the people's safety.

76
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,680
It may not have been

77
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:35,520
entirely foolish.

78
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:38,960
(Even with amnesia,
he's still defending himself.)

79
00:03:39,430 --> 00:03:41,310
(His survival instincts
are pretty strong.)

80
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,120
In front of me,

81
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:49,560
I make the rules.

82
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,870
Chou,

83
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:54,310
don't forget who you are.

84
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:57,280
You're my servant.

85
00:03:57,960 --> 00:04:00,400
That scoundrel destroyed your family.

86
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,910
You were left to wander the wilderness
like a dying stray dog.

87
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:04,870
I was the one who picked you up.

88
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:07,120
And now you're defending your enemy?

89
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,590
Don't forget

90
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:14,430
how you got that wound on your chest.

91
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,480
Tell me.

92
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:25,830
Who is he?

93
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,560
My

94
00:04:29,070 --> 00:04:29,720
enemy.

95
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,870
Louder.

96
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,070
Who is he?

97
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:37,240
My enemy!

98
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,040
That's more like it.

99
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:41,800
Keep reading.

100
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,680
Don't let me hear

101
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,560
even the slightest hesitation.

102
00:04:58,620 --> 00:05:00,340
(On the Foolish Deeds of the Scoundrel
Crown Prince Zheng Yuanhe)

103
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,390
That scoundrel Zheng Yuanhe,

104
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,040
though of noble rank,

105
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,390
is base in character.

106
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:08,120
He leads the criminal organization
known as the Inspectorate.

107
00:05:10,190 --> 00:05:12,780
The Inspectorate is responsible
for upholding the laws of the realm.

108
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,720
Calling it a criminal organization...

109
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,360
Is that...

110
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:20,190
You...

111
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:21,560
Have you lost your mind?

112
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:24,430
A law enforcement agency?

113
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,830
Did he pay for the rice balls
he took from me?

114
00:05:26,870 --> 00:05:28,270
If he didn't, that's robbery.

115
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:30,870
Why shouldn't a gang of robbers
be called a criminal organization?

116
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,830
Chou,

117
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,510
remember this.

118
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:38,160
In this world,

119
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:40,510
anyone who bullies me is a bad person.

120
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,510
Especially Zheng Yuanhe.

121
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:44,310
He's the worst of them all.

122
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,480
Your job

123
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,920
is to curse him and hate him.

124
00:05:50,270 --> 00:05:52,000
If one day

125
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:54,390
I really get the chance to kill him,

126
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,390
you'll

127
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,240
hand me the knife.

128
00:05:58,920 --> 00:05:59,630
Understand?

129
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:11,070
Understood.

130
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:12,360
That's more like it.

131
00:06:13,070 --> 00:06:13,950
Start over.

132
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:16,040
Put some feeling into it.

133
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:20,070
Read it with hatred deep in your bones.

134
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,430
That scoundrel Zheng Yuanhe

135
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:29,240
is petty, despicable,

136
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,680
and ruthless enough

137
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:34,270
to wipe out even a humble rice ball.

138
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:37,950
He's utterly blind and heartless,

139
00:06:38,070 --> 00:06:39,360
a vile little man.

140
00:06:41,310 --> 00:06:42,070
Good.

141
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:43,720
Well done.

142
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:47,600
As a reward, massage my legs.

143
00:07:11,870 --> 00:07:12,950
(Zheng Yuanhe...)

144
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:15,310
(Now that you're in my hands,)

145
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,680
(don't blame me
for making a fool of you.)

146
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,950
(You owe me this.)

147
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,430
All right.

148
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,430
Open up.

149
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,040
You may have lost your memory,

150
00:07:45,230 --> 00:07:47,160
but at least you haven't
gone completely stupid.

151
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,390
All right then.

152
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:50,160
Tomorrow,

153
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:54,070
start with how he led his men
to destroy my newspaper office,

154
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:56,120
and write an essay titled,

155
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:59,240
"Why Crown Prince Zheng Yuanhe

156
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,000
Is Doomed to Die Alone."

157
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,000
Make it insightful.

158
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,920
Make it hit him where it hurts.

159
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,310
Understand?

160
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:08,000
Yes.

161
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:11,430
Yes, Master.

162
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,510
Good.

163
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:14,270
Off you go.

164
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,720
Bring me some water for a foot bath.

165
00:08:30,190 --> 00:08:32,200
Miss, something has happened
at the Pan Residence.

166
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,480
What happened?

167
00:08:33,550 --> 00:08:36,150
Li Muyan took
your parents-in-law's property deed.

168
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:38,030
She found a black market broker
to sell it.

169
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,360
Li Muyan,

170
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,510
she really never learn.

171
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:42,390
Let's go.

172
00:08:42,410 --> 00:08:43,690
We're going back to deal with her.

173
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:47,420
(Pan Residence)

174
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:02,030
Qingqing, why are you angry
the moment you get back?

175
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,200
Besides,

176
00:09:04,870 --> 00:09:06,440
the way he's looking at me

177
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,960
is rather scary.

178
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,390
Stop pretending.

179
00:09:10,060 --> 00:09:12,780
Did you trick them out of the property deed
and try to sell it on the black market?

180
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,550
I...

181
00:09:14,620 --> 00:09:16,600
I don't know
what you're talking about, Qingqing.

182
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:18,840
Still pretending?

183
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:22,150
Looks like getting beaten
by the Second Prince

184
00:09:22,150 --> 00:09:23,670
didn't teach you a lesson.

185
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:27,670
I won't let you keep making
a mess of the Pan Residence.

186
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:28,600
What are you doing?

187
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:30,600
I'm the head of the Pan family.

188
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,000
You?

189
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:34,320
Ever since you came back from Beicang,

190
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:36,390
you haven't had a proper job.

191
00:09:36,410 --> 00:09:37,840
Everything this household eats,
wears, and uses

192
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,440
is paid for with my money.

193
00:09:40,050 --> 00:09:42,990
And you still have the nerve to call yourself
the head of the Pan family?

194
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,960
Starting today,

195
00:09:49,020 --> 00:09:51,550
the authority to run this household
and the keys to the treasury

196
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,960
will all be under my control.

197
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,080
Without my token,

198
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,390
no one,

199
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:00,510
including Pan Yang and Li Muyan,

200
00:10:00,810 --> 00:10:02,910
may withdraw a single coin
from the accounts office.

201
00:10:03,150 --> 00:10:03,870
You...

202
00:10:04,510 --> 00:10:06,790
A woman wants to run the household?

203
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:07,910
Qingqing,

204
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,390
are you trying to starve us?

205
00:10:09,630 --> 00:10:10,840
If you have a problem with it,

206
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:12,790
take it up with my sword.

207
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:19,390
Let's go.

208
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:21,080
Let's hand over the accounts.

209
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:25,480
I...

210
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,200
Yang...

211
00:10:35,660 --> 00:10:37,100
(Ledger)
Miss,

212
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,630
we've moved over
the Pan Residence account books

213
00:10:38,630 --> 00:10:40,360
and all the silver.

214
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:43,270
Good. Move everything into the treasury.

215
00:10:44,030 --> 00:10:45,510
Is this your plan, Miss,

216
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:47,360
to keep the Pan family's
money under lock and key?

217
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,870
Not keep it under lock and key.

218
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:51,240
This is called
proper financial management.

219
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:53,440
The old free-for-all

220
00:10:53,750 --> 00:10:54,510
is over.

221
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,080
Miss,

222
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,120
Li Muyan's people

223
00:10:58,120 --> 00:11:00,240
came to collect this month's allowance.

224
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:01,840
They're asking for fifty taels

225
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:03,440
to buy cosmetics.

226
00:11:03,870 --> 00:11:05,200
Fifty taels?

227
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,840
How much makeup
does she need to spend fifty taels?

228
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:08,630
Denied.

229
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:11,270
Natural beauty is true beauty.

230
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:12,750
Wash your face with rice water.

231
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:19,960
Miss, one more thing.

232
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:23,240
The General said he needs
three hundred taels for expenses.

233
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:24,080
For expenses?

234
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:26,480
I wonder what he's really planning.

235
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,170
The top courtesan
at the Zuichun House, perhaps?

236
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,200
Denied.

237
00:11:29,630 --> 00:11:31,870
He may be unemployed now,

238
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,000
but he was once a general.

239
00:11:34,790 --> 00:11:37,630
He should lead by example.

240
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:38,120
Yes.

241
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,550
I'll let them know.

242
00:11:40,270 --> 00:11:40,840
Let's go.

243
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:57,550
Li Qingqing

244
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,670
actually dared to do this.

245
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:04,360
Young Master, forgive me
for speaking out of turn.

246
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:07,030
Madam is the matriarch
of the Pan family.

247
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,550
The treasury keys

248
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,440
should indeed be in Madam's hands.

249
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,480
The matriarch...

250
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,600
No wonder she pulled this stunt.

251
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:22,960
She's trying to win back

252
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,870
her place in my heart.

253
00:12:28,390 --> 00:12:29,870
Women...

254
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:34,000
They only know how to fight for my favor
with these household tricks.

255
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,200
Fine.

256
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:40,790
If she cares so much
about my attitude toward her,

257
00:12:41,630 --> 00:12:43,150
then I

258
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:44,360
shall grant her wish.

259
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:57,200
Qingqing,

260
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,270
you're still busy this late?

261
00:13:01,570 --> 00:13:02,790
If you have something to say, say it.

262
00:13:02,790 --> 00:13:03,600
If not, leave.

263
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:04,550
There you go again.

264
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,960
Still as stubborn as ever.

265
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:09,320
That's what I admire about you.

266
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:14,870
Have you lost your mind?

267
00:13:15,630 --> 00:13:16,790
No.

268
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:19,600
Qingqing,

269
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:21,910
these past few days,

270
00:13:22,630 --> 00:13:24,120
I've given it a lot of thought.

271
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:28,360
I was a fool before.

272
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:32,000
Li Muyan completely bewitched me.

273
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,600
But now I understand.

274
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:39,030
You're the wife I married properly.

275
00:13:39,630 --> 00:13:42,510
You should be the matriarch
of the Pan family.

276
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,240
So?

277
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,080
So...

278
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:55,120
I'm willing to give you a chance

279
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:57,200
to come back to my side.

280
00:13:57,550 --> 00:13:58,750
You'll still be my legal wife.

281
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,910
As for Muyan,

282
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,390
I'll talk to her myself.

283
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:05,120
And the child she's carrying,

284
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:09,360
once it's born, you'll raise it

285
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:10,960
as its birth mother.

286
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:12,790
What could be better than that?

287
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:16,390
Are you short on money?

288
00:14:16,450 --> 00:14:18,320
Is that why you're here
acting like a lapdog?

289
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:20,080
Li Qingqing,

290
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:22,360
I'm willing to take you back

291
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:24,510
because you're good at making money
and managing the accounts.

292
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:25,840
Don't be so ungrateful.

293
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:30,000
I know you still have feelings for me.

294
00:14:31,030 --> 00:14:32,770
That's why
I'm willing to accept you again.

295
00:14:33,270 --> 00:14:35,440
You should be grateful.

296
00:14:38,910 --> 00:14:39,550
Muyan.

297
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,960
Didn't I tell you to get some rest?

298
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:41,750
Why are you here?

299
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:43,790
If I stayed away any longer,

300
00:14:43,870 --> 00:14:45,750
this vixen would steal you away.

301
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,840
When did you ever see me
trying to seduce him?

302
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,000
You picked up a piece of trash
and treated it like a treasure.

303
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,990
Don't assume everyone else
likes collecting trash like you do.

304
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:52,720
Who are you calling trash?

305
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:53,320
You!

306
00:14:53,630 --> 00:14:55,390
Stop acting so high and mighty.

307
00:14:55,550 --> 00:14:56,750
Don't think I don't know.

308
00:14:56,760 --> 00:14:58,150
You're trying to marry
into the royal family

309
00:14:58,150 --> 00:14:59,790
and become His Highness's woman.

310
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,750
Why don't you look in the mirror?

311
00:15:01,770 --> 00:15:04,290
Do you really think the royal family
would want someone like you?

312
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:06,240
So that's what you really think.

313
00:15:08,150 --> 00:15:10,150
Face reality.

314
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:11,750
Who is His Highness?

315
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:12,840
And who are you?

316
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:14,720
You'd be better off staying with me.

317
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:15,670
Jiuzhu,

318
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:17,240
throw them both out.

319
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,150
Where's Jiuzhu?

320
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:22,960
Hey! Easy!

321
00:15:27,150 --> 00:15:28,960
Just looking at those two makes me sick.

322
00:15:33,470 --> 00:15:35,120
Zheng Yuanhe
has already lost his memory.

323
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:36,690
Why should I stay here
and keep putting up with them?

324
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:38,000
Pack everything up.

325
00:15:38,190 --> 00:15:39,550
We'll move on an auspicious day.

326
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,000
All right.

327
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:41,510
No.

328
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:43,720
Why should I be the one moving?

329
00:15:43,870 --> 00:15:44,840
Tell those two

330
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:46,120
to get out.

331
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:47,240
My parents-in-law can stay.

332
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:47,840
Yes.

333
00:15:49,300 --> 00:15:51,190
How have our earnings been
these past few days?

334
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:54,960
The rice balls made by the Crown Prince,

335
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:56,390
and the flower business

336
00:15:56,550 --> 00:15:58,200
only made this much.

337
00:15:58,260 --> 00:16:02,060
(Ledger)

338
00:16:02,390 --> 00:16:04,200
Why is there so little money?

339
00:16:04,590 --> 00:16:06,550
It's not even enough
to rent a proper storefront.

340
00:16:08,150 --> 00:16:09,670
It's all Zheng Yuanhe's fault.

341
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:12,120
He wiped out all my savings.

342
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:16,960
Still,

343
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,840
heaven always leaves a way out.

344
00:16:21,750 --> 00:16:22,360
Caiyuan.

345
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:24,550
Do you know who in the capital

346
00:16:24,550 --> 00:16:26,870
has the most money
and the most free time,

347
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:28,630
and is willing to spend it?

348
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:32,720
Government officials?

349
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:33,440
Wrong.

350
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:36,000
The wealthy ladies.

351
00:16:36,010 --> 00:16:38,190
They're the real driving force
behind consumer spending.

352
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:42,550
Tower Master, you've come up
with another good idea?

353
00:16:44,030 --> 00:16:45,630
Don't we already have a boy band?

354
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:49,320
And two ready-made top male models.

355
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:53,510
We'd be fools not to use them.

356
00:17:04,380 --> 00:17:07,740
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

357
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:11,900
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

358
00:17:12,660 --> 00:17:14,420
♪Your smile♪

359
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:16,940
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

360
00:17:16,940 --> 00:17:20,620
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

361
00:17:21,100 --> 00:17:24,420
♪Yet I stand before you♪

362
00:17:25,140 --> 00:17:28,980
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

363
00:17:29,380 --> 00:17:31,300
♪Though fate tries♪

364
00:17:31,300 --> 00:17:33,900
♪To make us pass each other by♪

365
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:37,540
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

366
00:17:37,780 --> 00:17:39,420
♪Though time slips by♪

367
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:41,180
♪As day turns into night♪

368
00:17:41,700 --> 00:17:45,740
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

369
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:48,540
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

370
00:17:48,540 --> 00:17:50,300
♪Blessed by fate♪

371
00:17:50,300 --> 00:17:55,460
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

372
00:17:55,460 --> 00:17:57,900
♪Your smiling face♪

373
00:17:57,900 --> 00:18:00,740
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

374
00:18:00,740 --> 00:18:04,380
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

375
00:18:04,900 --> 00:18:08,340
♪And wander the world together♪

376
00:18:08,340 --> 00:18:09,700
♪Holding you close♪

377
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:12,220
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

378
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:14,540
♪Your tenderness♪

379
00:18:14,540 --> 00:18:17,420
♪Is the brightest moon♪

380
00:18:17,420 --> 00:18:21,100
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

381
00:18:21,620 --> 00:18:24,940
♪Our love will never fade away♪

382
00:18:24,940 --> 00:18:27,380
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

383
00:18:27,900 --> 00:18:32,180
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

384
00:18:41,660 --> 00:18:43,820
♪Your smiling face♪

385
00:18:43,980 --> 00:18:46,580
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

386
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:50,740
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

387
