♪And wander the world together♪

388
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:55,780
♪Holding you close♪

389
00:18:55,780 --> 00:18:58,420
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

390
00:18:58,420 --> 00:19:00,700
♪Your tenderness♪

391
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:03,540
♪Is the brightest moon♪

392
00:19:03,540 --> 00:19:07,300
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

393
00:19:07,740 --> 00:19:11,100
♪Our love will never fade away♪

394
